<%def name="h1_content()" filter="trim">
${_(u'About OpenFisca')}
</%def>


<%def name="page_content()" filter="trim">
        <p>
            OpenFisca is a free simulation software for the French socio-fiscal system. It allows users to easily visualise a great number of taxes and benefits, and to simulate the impact of reforms on their households revenue. It is a educational tool whose aim is to help citizens better understand France's socio-fiscal system.
        </p>
        <p>
            In the long run, OpenFisca will model the entire socio-fiscal system as well as it's progression. It will also be used to calculate the impact of various reforms on the state budget.
        </p>

